VUNERABILITY / EXPLOIT
======================

Local:
------
Passwords and user names are stored cleartext inside registry under
Windows OS


REG Key
Subkey ( data )

HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\VB and VBA Program
Settings\GrubClient\Settings
userEmail
userPassword


Vendor Fix:
-----------
upgrade to..
grub-client-1.4.3


